## When to Load Full Mind

- Extended work sessions
- Cross-referencing multiple concepts
- Entity relationship analysis
- Historical context needed
- Writing documentation that references multiple sources

## Loading Options

**Full graph (expensive):**
Load all files in concepts/ and entities/

**Selective (recommended):**
Load SKILL.md + specific files as needed

**Progressive:**
1. Start with nexus-core (hot reference)
2. Expand to nexus-mind files as topics arise
3. Let gremlin-brain reference tables guide lookups

